// The Buffalo fold applies absolute value to both components of z⁶ after the
// power. This post-power bilateral fold creates six-armed structures where
// each arm features buffalo-horn curvature and deeply nested spiral tangles.
// Smooth coloring: log₂(6). Supports normal-map shading (colorScheme 50-63).
